# encrypt352 Readme
### ajharms

## src/supplied/
Files supplied for the assignment go here to be compiled into the application

## src/threads/encrypt352.c
Main thread of the application.

## src/threads/threads
The other threads for the application.

## src/util/bools
Simplifies conditionals and helps readability by
declaring 1 and 0 as true and false and typedefing booleans.

## src/util/buffer
Buffer for handling the threads in a thread safe way.  Only holds the characters,
doesn't do any of the other work for them.

## src/utils/errors
Methods for printing error. Keeps track of exit statuses.

## src/utils/print_counts
Prints the output for the counts to the terminal.